<h1>You've been invited to FlexiLabour</h1>

<p><%= @invited_by_name %> has invited <strong><%= @agency.name %></strong> to join FlexiLabour, a flexible staff management platform.</p>

<p>Click the link below to register your agency account:</p>

<p>
  <a href="<%= @registration_url %>" style="display:inline-block;padding:10px 20px;background:#570df8;color:#fff;text-decoration:none;border-radius:6px;">
    Register Your Agency
  </a>
</p>

<p>Or copy this link into your browser:</p>
<p><%= @registration_url %></p>

<hr>

<p style="color:#888;font-size:12px;">
  This invitation was sent on behalf of <%= @invited_by_name %>. If you were not expecting this invitation, you can ignore this email.
</p>
